{"id":370906,"date":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":16}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"277","ytitle":"","mtitle":"沽河谣(莱阳)","ftitle":"","authors":["刘饶民"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘饶民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖河道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖河道，加劲干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万张铁锨如闪电。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖得河道丈把深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看谁是英雄汉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旱天沽河不断流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涝天沽河不汜滥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年河上跑木筏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明年开来小轮船。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变了样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沽河水，闪金浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沽河边，变了样:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青菜满园绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谷子满野香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鹅鸭满池塘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛羊满山岗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道上的汽车<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1958\\06\\586g0307AA.JPG\"><IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1958\\06\\586g0307AA.JPG\">响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜里的电灯耀眼亮……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修堤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推出车，套上牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去到山上拉石头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉青石，拉黑石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉了石头修河堤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉一趟，又一趟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修起大堤像城墙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铜墙坚，铜墙高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪水涨不到半中腰!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抽水机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抽水机，河边按，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抽来河水喷上山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇梨花，白皑皑；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇桃花，红艳艳；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇棉花，银闪闪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇稻子，金灿灿……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄稼人喜得大声笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沽河也喜得浪花翻。"}]}